<plot>A deadly game of cat and mouse ensues when a bus carrying local convicts crashes near a secluded mountain home that belongs to Amy, a blind teen. The worst part? The lead con, Roy, decides to hide in Amy's cabin, right under her nose. Now it's up to Amy to figure out exactly what's going down and stop this lunatic before her time runs out!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?343848</url></doc>
